article.description: — Mitchell Sueker had 15 points in North Dakota's 77-73 win over Elon on Thursday.
article.headline: North Dakota defeats Elon 77-73
article.story: ELON, N.C. -- — Mitchell Sueker had 15 points in North Dakota's 77-73 win over Elon on Thursday. Sueker added nine rebounds and five assists for the Fightin' Hawks (2-2). Treysen Eaglestaff scored 15 points, going 6 of 10 (3 for 6 from distance). B.J. Omot recorded 12 points and was 3 of 11 shooting, including 2 for 8 from distance, and went 4 for 4 from the line. Sean Halloran led the way for the Phoenix (1-3) with 21 points. Zac Ervin added 15 points for Elon. Torrence Watson also had 12 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
